programme.desc: Desa Alam Endah di Kampung Ciburial Ciwidey yang jaraknya 37km dari kota Bandung ini terkenal kerana iklimnya yang sederhana sejuk kerana kawasan ini berdekatan dengan kawasan pergunungan yang tingginya lebih 1500 meter di atas paras air laut - juga terkenal dengan pondok belajar mengaji, Pesantren Al Ittifaq diasaskan oleh Kiai Hj Mansur pada 1934, dan diteruskan oleh keturunan beliau sendiri iaitu Kiai Hj Fuad Affendi.

programme.title: Religious Clip S70 Ep10
programme.desc: Dalam episod kali ini, topik yang di sampaikan ialah Bagaimana Mahu Istiqamah. programme.title: Setia Menunggumu Ep7
programme.desc: Sebelum Adi berangkat, Adi telah memberitahu kenalan rapat nya yang dia akan pergi mencari ilmu agama jauh dari sini. Adi mengambil bas dan sampai ke pekan, sampai di pekan dia cuba menahan kereta yang lalu lalang, kemudian ada sebuah lori yang baik hati memberi dia tumpang sampai ke KL. Sampai sahaja di KL, Adi tidak tahu dia mahu pergi ke mana, lalu dia jumpa sebuah masjid tetapi dia tidak solat kerana Adi tidak tahu solat. Selesai habis solat di masjid itu, dia bertanyakan dari Imam masjid tersebut tentang cara untuk mempelajari ilmu agama. Imam tersebut telah memberikan nya nombor telefon seorang pemuda.

programme.title: Pinjaman Kepada Allah

programme.title: Resort Berhantu
programme.desc: Sekumpulan rakan bersepakat untuk membuli Rosalinda buat kali terakhir, namun rancangan mereka mula bertukar apabila melihat mayat Rosalinda terapung di dalam kolam. Mereka mula ketakutan kerana dihantui oleh jelmaan hantu Rosalinda.

programme.title: Jamu Nesan Ep14
programme.desc: Madam Seow jumpa Sunny Lee dan merayu agar Sunny mengembalikan perniagaannya semula tetapi Sunny Lee tidak bersetuju. Empayar dadah Madam Zoora semakin meluas apabila Samat membawa King Pin iaitu mafia daripada Siam. Misi Madam Zoora untuk meluaskan empayar dadahnya hampir berjaya. Dia menjadi pembekal dadah utama mereka di Siam. Madam Zoora pula terus memburu Fendy kerana cuba membunuh Tok Chai dan Big Bro diarahkan untuk memburu Fendy.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S16 Ep5

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep13
programme.desc: Farah tidak mampu lagi memaafkan Lukman apabila sekali lagi bertembung dengan Myra di dalam rumah Lukman. Seluruh kepercayaan sudah lerai. Dia keluar dari rumah dan enggan berjumpa dengan Lukman lagi. Dia sanggup tinggal di hotel demi menjauhkan diri daripada semua orang. Lukman resah apabila tidak dapat mencari Farah namun hal itu disembunyikan daripada familinya. Segalanya berpunca daripada Myra yang datang ke rumah demi mengadukan konon dirinya teraniaya. Pihak pengurusan syarikat mendapat bukti bahawa Lukman terbabit dalam kehilangan wang syarikat. Abah tidak percaya dengan tindakan Farah yang nekad ke UK meninggalkan suami dan Zahin. Budi mengesyaki ada yang tak kena dengan kes Lukman. Farah pula menanggalkan cincin perkahwinan lalu diserahkan kepada Lukman. Dia sudah redha apa sahaja jalinan takdirnya. programme.desc: Sepanjang berada di UK, Farah diasak rindu terhadap Lukman dan Zahin. programme.title: Dihatiku Ada Kamu Ep26

Rian bersyukur Adif tidak menceraikannya. Hubungan mereka kembali baik dan Rian sedari keikhlasan Adif tapi berlaku salah faham pula apabila Rian dengar perbualan telefon Adif dengan seseorang. Rian sangka Adif nak perangkap dia saja. Rian larikan diri. Adif cuba terangkan sekali lagi sehingga kali ini Adif sudah putus asa sebab Rian masih tak percayakannya. Adif beri syarat jika Rian pergi, akan jatuh satu talak. Dan Rian pergi dengan rasa amat sedih. Idris beritahu, Rian dan Adif salah faham. idris percaya Adif lebih daripada Rian. Adif datang. Adif terangkan. apa yang Rian dengar malam tadi adalah untuk stalker iaitu Fitrin, bukan Rian. Adif jelaskan tentang manipulasi Fitrin. Fitrin datang serang mereka tanpa mereka jangka sehingga tertikam Adif semasa Adif nak selamatkan Rian. Afeeq juga sedar Fitrin telah pergunakan dia juga. Fitrin dapat ditangkap. Hujung kisah proses rujuk semula antara Rian dan Adif setelah masing masing tidak dapat hidup sendiri dan dihat mereka masih ada cinta antara sesama mereka.

programme.title: Araf 5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang wanita muda yang mendapati dirinya dalam mimpi ngeri yang mengerikan ketika cuba menyara keluarga bekas teman lelakinya yang membunuhnya. Zeynep, seorang wanita muda, kecewa apabila dia mengetahui bahawa bekas teman lelakinya Kadir membunuhnya dengan cara digantung. Mengucapkan takziah kepada keluarga Kadir, Zeynep memutuskan untuk tinggal bersama mereka selama beberapa hari untuk menyara mereka atas desakan ibu Kadir. Bagaimanapun, tiada apa yang dilihat di dalam rumah itu menggambarkan kebenaran. Dalam proses ini, Zeynep mengetahui tentang kematian Kadir daripada entiti yang menghantui rumah itu. Diseret ke dalam pusaran, Zeynep mendapati dirinya di tengah-tengah Api Penyucian, tempat antara dua alam.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Plan B Ep12
programme.desc: Mengisahkan pasukan polis mengepung premis awam di mana Khai dan Iris bersembunyi dan menculik beberapa perkerja sebagai tebusan. Sebelum ini Mika yang cedera di dada akibat ditembak polis turut berada dalam premis itu. Que dibawa oleh Inspektor Faris untuk berunding dengan Khai supaya membebaskan tebusan. Khai hanya membebaskan dua tebusan setelah syarat menyerahkan Que kepadanya dipenuhi. Kedua-dua ibu bapa Khai dan Mika turut berada di tempat kejadian itu. Setelah mengubah aliran CCTV, beberapa anggota polis berjaya merempuh masuk ke premis itu. Khai, Iris, Que dan Mika diberkas polis.

programme.title: Zerk
programme.desc: Fatma, yang kehilangan anak perempuannya akibat lemas di tasik, selepas beberapa ketika, menyangka bahawa anak perempuannya belum meninggal dunia dan mengambil anak perempuannya dari kuburnya dan membawanya pulang. Wanita itu, yang hilang keseimbangan mental pada siang hari, membunuh diri dengan menggantung diri.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep4
programme.desc: Ketegangan meningkat di majlis hari jadi Elyn apabila Din dihina dan dihalau, mengakibatkan konflik yang berterusan berlaku antara ayah dan anak.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep5
programme.desc: Ashikin membantu Uzair melarikan diri daripada Imran tetapi menerima akibatnya. Uzair tertarik dengan Noramina. Imran kecewa kerana Madi belum sedar daripada koma. Janice berputus asa dengan Ashikin. Perlawanan yang telah diatur dari mula, Uzair kalah dalam perlawanan timbal balik kepada Hatta. Imran perlu berunding tentang perebutan kawasan dengan seorang lelaki misteri bernama Along.

programme.title: Alam Puaka Ep4
programme.desc: Kisah-kisah yang dipaparkan di dalam siri ini adalah berdasarkan daripada penceritaan masyarakat umum. Ianya dilakonkan secara fiksyen dan sebarang penambahan tidak berkaitan dengan sesiapa samada hidup atau telah meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil 2
programme.desc: Kisah mengenai Fadil yang terjerumus ke dalam dunia mafia yang diketuai oleh Taji Samprit dan anaknya, Wak Doyok. Satu insiden menyebabkan Inspektor Wahab dan Inspektor Shuib mengesyaki Fadil sebagai Tiger, seorang pembunuh upahan profesional.

programme.title: Rampok
programme.desc: Seorang wanita bersenjata merompak bank dan menjadikan mereka yang berada dalam bank sebagai orang tebusan. Pihak polis berunding dan wanita tersebut bersetuju untuk melepaskan tebusan tanpa pihak polis mengetahui bahawa orang tebusan tersebut merupakan perompak dan rakan perompak itu sendiri.

programme.title: Congkak
programme.desc: Kisahnya bermula apabila Kazman serta isterinya Sufiah mengambil keputusan bercuti bersama dua anaknya, Lisa dan Ely di sebuah banglo di tepi tasik. Kazman sudah berjanji dengan seorang kawannya untuk membeli banglo tersebut sebagai persinggahan semasa bercuti. Pelbagai peristiwa pelik berlaku sepanjang perjalan mereka termasuk kehilangan telefon bimbitnya. Setibanya mereka di banglo tersebut, peristiwa yang semakin pelik turut terjadi. Sufiah cuba meyakinkan Kazman untuk keluar dari rumah tersebut tetapi tidak diendahkan. Kazman tetap berkeras untuk membeli rumah tersebut kerana sudah berjanji dengan kawannya. Sufiah sentiasa merasakan ada makhluk sedang memerhatikannya. Salah seorang anak mereka, Lisa setiap malam akan turun ke sebuah bilik gelap untuk bermain congkak dengan seseorang yang hanya boleh dilihat olehnya seorang. Sufiah yang tidak boleh bersabar dengan perkara itu telah membuang congkak tersebut ke dalam tasik. Lisa juga sentiasa bermain di tepi belukar di belakang rumah kerana kawannya tinggal di situ sehingga Kazman perasan Lisa bermain menghadap kubur lama. Pada malam keesokannya, Sufiah dikejutkan lagi dengan bunyi congkak tersebut dari bilik yang sama. Apabila Sufiah pergi melihat, dilihatnya seorang tua sedang bemain congkak tersebut. Semakin lama peristiwa yang berlaku semakin pelik dan menyeramkan sehingga pada malam ketiga kedua-dua anaknya telah hilang dan Sufiah didapati tidur di siling bilik. Pak Tua, penduduk paling lama di kampung itu telah pergi ke rumah tersebut untuk menyelamatkan keluarga Kazman dan mencari Ely dan Lisa. Apakah sejarah sebenar banglo tersebut dan dapatkan Sufiah diselamatkan serta berjayakah Ely dan Lisa ditemui semula.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil 1
programme.desc: Abang Long Fadil, seorang lelaki yang sentiasa berangan bahawa kehidupannya seperti seorang gangster. Namun, apabila sahabat baiknya, Malik, dimasukkan ke penjara, keadaan menjadi lebih huru-hara, dan angan-angannya mungkin tidak jauh daripada realiti.

programme.title: Cinderella's Curse
programme.desc: Cinderella, dalam keadaan terdesak, memanggil ibu pari-parinya melalui sebuah kitab kuno yang terikat dengan kulit manusia, dengan harapan untuk menuntut keadilan dan membalas dendam terhadap ibu tiri dan kakak tirinya yang sentiasa menyeksa serta menindasnya tanpa henti.

programme.title: Ong Bak 2
programme.desc: Berlatarkan Thailand abad ke-15, filem ini berkisarkan Tien, anak kepada seorang bangsawan yang dibunuh. Ditawan dan dijual sebagai hamba, Tien diselamatkan daripada kematian oleh Chernang, ketua Pha Beek Khrut, sekumpulan artis mempertahankan diri yang pakar dalam pelbagai gaya tempur Asia.

programme.title: Two Sisters
programme.desc: Selepas seorang gadis dibebaskan dari rumah sakit jiwa, dia disatukan semula dengan kakaknya dan mereka kembali ke rumah keluarga yang ditinggalkan. Namun, kedua-dua beradik itu menyimpan rahsia gelap dan tragis keluarga yang mula terungkap selepas kepulangan mereka.

programme.title: Bini-bini Ku Gangster
programme.desc: Manja dan Herry adalah sepasang suami isteri yang sangat romantik dan saling sayang menyayangi. Tanpa disedari oleh Herry, Manja adalah ketua kumpulan kepada sebuah geng gengster di Kuala Lumpur. Di pejabat,Herry kerap dibuli Mat Saja termasuk menyuruh Herry menggantikan tempatnya semasa ulangtahun perkahwinan Manja dan Herry yang ke2. Manja bengang lalu menghantar orang-orangnya memukul Mat Saja.

programme.title: Ong Bak 3
programme.desc: Kisah pahlawan Tien, yang telah ditangkap oleh panglima perang yang kejam Tuan Rajasena. Tien melarikan diri daripada cengkaman Rajasena, pulih daripada kecederaannya yang melumpuhkan dengan bantuan Guru Bua, dan kembali untuk berhadapan dengan Bhuti Sangkha, yang telah menggantikan Rajasena sebagai penjahat utama.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep5
programme.desc: Seorang pembunuh upahan sedang menjejakinya lalu Black menyedari masanya dalam badan Malik semakin suntuk. Dia mesti menamatkan misinya dengan cepat dan satu-satunya harapan yang dia ada adalah menyakinkan Sofia untuk membantunya. Dia terjumpa sebuah bilik rahsia di dalam rumah Malik di mana tersimpan barang-barang yang jelas sekali disorok oleh Malik. Sementara itu, Sofia nampak satu pembunuhan bakal berlaku yang mengganggu perasaannya sehingga merangsang dia untuk bertindak. Dia memujuk Black untuk pulang ke kampung halaman mereka di Seri Setia untuk menyiasat kes itu. Anehnya, penyiasatan Borhan ke atas kes Nurul Najwa juga membawanya ke Seri Setia. Di sana, dia ketemu semula rakan sekerja lamanya, yang menyimpan rahsia tentang kes dingin yang berlaku 20 tahun lalu.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep3
programme.desc: Din Tiger berusaha mencari kebenaran di sebalik kematian isterinya, tetapi keadaan bertambah rumit akibat penyelewengan yang dilakukan oleh Anat terbongkar.

programme.desc: Mengisahkan setelah Que bebas dari tahanan polis, dia menasihati Khai dan Cika tidak meneruskan niat mereka untuk mengadakan lumba kereta secara haram, kerana polis sedang menjejaki aktiviti mereka. Khai pula berdepan dengan masalah kewangan, kerana ayahnya telah memberhentikan pemberian wang poket kepadanya dan dia juga banyak berhutang dengan Cika, membuatkan Khai seringkali bertelagah dan bersikap kasar dengan ayahnya. Que ingin membantu mententeramkan jiwa Khai, walaupun ibunya, menegah Que bercampur gaul dengan Khai dan lain-lain, tetapi Que terpaksa membantu Khai dengan alasan bahawa mereka sekeluarga telah terhutang budi dengan keluarga Khai.

programme.title: Araf 5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang wanita muda yang mendapati dirinya dalam mimpi ngeri yang mengerikan ketika cuba menyara keluarga bekas teman lelakinya yang membunuhnya. Zeynep, seorang wanita muda, kecewa apabila dia mengetahui bahawa bekas teman lelakinya Kadir membunuhnya dengan cara digantung. Mengucapkan takziah kepada keluarga Kadir, Zeynep memutuskan untuk tinggal bersama mereka selama beberapa hari untuk menyara mereka atas desakan ibu Kadir. Bagaimanapun, tiada apa yang dilihat di dalam rumah itu menggambarkan kebenaran. Dalam proses ini, Zeynep mengetahui tentang kematian Kadir daripada entiti yang menghantui rumah itu. Diseret ke dalam pusaran, Zeynep mendapati dirinya di tengah-tengah Api Penyucian, tempat antara dua alam.

programme.desc: 5 pelajar pergi ke lawatan sekolah di Pulau Karantina untuk kelas Sejarah. Tetapi salah seorang daripada mereka akan tersesat ke hospital terbiar dan rakan sekelasnya perlu mencarinya, menghadapi ancaman paranormal di sepanjang jalan.

programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: Kapsul
programme.desc: Kapsul masa wawasan 2020 yang ditanam oleh Tun Dr. Mahathir Mohamad telah dicuri dan membawa Zohri kembali ke masa lalu. Zohri kini terperangkap di tengah-tengah pergolakan bangsa Melayu untuk mencapai kemerdekaan dan membawa bangsa Melayu keluar dari belenggu kemiskinan. Zohri melihat dan merasai sendiri erti perjuangan umatnya yang tidak pernah dibayangkannya selama ini. Dia lihat, dia rasa dan kini dia mula faham betapa peritnya liku-liku sejarah negara dan bangsa. Perjalanan Zohri berterusan dari satu zaman ke satu zaman dan tiada siapa yang dapat mengembalikannya ke zamannya melainkan dirinya sendiri.

programme.title: Fobia Malam Pertama
programme.desc: Fobia Malam Pertama menceritakan tentang Zaty, pelajar sebuah kolej tempatan di Pulau Pinang yang fobia untuk bercinta.

programme.title: Plan B Ep11
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Mika, Khai dan Iris dikejar polis. Mereka berjaya menyembunyikan diri dalam salah sebuah kedai motorsikal dan menawan seluruh pekerja kedai itu. Dalam keadaan cedera parah ditembak, Mika mengarahkan Khai memeriksa beg yang dirompak mereka. Setelah membukanya, Khai mendapati beg itu mengandungi bungkusan coklat yang dibalut dengan kertas warna keemasan. Kemudian pasukan polis berjaya mengempung lokasi persembunyian mereka. Que yang turut ditahan polis, dibawa bersama untuk memujuk kawan-kawannya menyerah diri.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep4
programme.desc: Ketegangan meningkat di majlis hari jadi Elyn apabila Din dihina dan dihalau, mengakibatkan konflik yang berterusan berlaku antara ayah dan anak.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep5
programme.desc: Ashikin membantu Uzair melarikan diri daripada Imran tetapi menerima akibatnya. Uzair tertarik dengan Noramina. Imran kecewa kerana Madi belum sedar daripada koma. Imran perlu berunding tentang perebutan kawasan dengan seorang lelaki misteri bernama Along.

programme.title: Pelepas Saka
programme.desc: Sejak pulang ke kampung, Alisya sering diganggu dengan bayangan seorang wanita tua dan kadang-kala dia akan mendengar bunyi buaian yang berayun di luar rumah. Alisya juga sering diganggu dengan mimpi yang bukan-bukan menyebabkan dia terfikir-fikir apa yang sedang terjadi padanya. Suatu malam, usai saja majlis doa selamat di rumah Adnan, Asiah telah melakukan upacara melepaskan sakanya pada Haider. Setelah melepaskan sakanya, wajah Asiah berubah menjadi sangat tua dan badannya membongkok. Asiah hilang jejak selepas itu. Haider tidak menyedari bahawa dirinya kini didampingi oleh saka Asiah dan perangainya mula berubah. Dia menjadi panas-baran, suka makan telur mentah, sentiasa panas dan mula mengsyaki hubungan antara Raden dan Alisya. Raden juga diganggu oleh saka Asiah dengan menjelmakan diri sebagai Alisya. Raden mula tidak sedap hati dan memberitahu hal ini pada Adnan. Raden juga berusaha mencari punca setiap gangguan yang berlaku di rumah tersebut sehingga membawanya ke rumah Asiah. Di situ barulah Raden tahu tentang kisah yang terjadi.

programme.title: Tembus
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hari yang memegang tanggungjawab besar dalam mengotakan janji agar kehidupan rumahtangganya menjadi semakin baik. Di mata masyarakat, Hari dan isterinya, Izza dianggap sebagai pasangan ideal yang sukses dalam hal rumahtangga dan kerjaya. Namun mereka diuji dengan kehilangan anak dan pelbagai rahsia terbongkar akibat terjadinya peristiwa itu.

programme.title: XX Ray 2
programme.desc: Bekerja sebagai saintis kadet, Tina berasa ditipu apabila Johan mendakwa dia yang mencipta mesin pelupusan laser walhal ia merupakan hasil cetusan idea dari Tina. Ingin menghalang niat jahat Johan, Tina meminta bantuan Amir. Namun, keduanya terkena pancaran laser mesin itu dalam cubaan untuk menghalang Johan dan telah dihantar ke zaman Kesultanan Melayu Melaka.

programme.title: Satu Impian
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Indra yang berhasrat untuk bekerja di bandar untuk membantu ibunya yang telah tua. Setelah mendapat restu ibunya, Indra mencari pekerjaan di bandar dengan bertemu Dato Karim rakan baik arwah bapanya. Indra diterima bekerja dan diminta untuk tinggal di rumah Dato Karim. Pada mulanya kehadiran Indra tidak disenangi Sandra, anak Dato Karim. Namun hubungan mereka semakin baik selepas Indra menyelamatkan Sandra daripada samseng jalanan. Pada masa yang sama, terdapat satu gerakan yang ingin mensabotaj projek yang sedang diuruskan syarikat Dato Karim.

programme.title: Bujang Selamat
programme.desc: Sering diganggu budak-budak di kampung, Bujang mula mempelajari ilmu persilatan. Bujang pergi mendaftarkan diri untuk bertanding di satu pertandingan silat namun telah diperli budak-budak lain. Rasa terhina, Bujang pun pergi bertemu seorang guru silat. Bersama guru itu, Bujang mempelajari teknik bersilat yang sangat hebat.

programme.title: Kau,Aku Dan Dia
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nancy dan Syafiq yang baru tamat pengajian di universiti. Walaupun berlainan bangsa, namun mereka saling mencintai antara satu sama lain. Konflik mula berlaku apabila orang tua ingin menjodohkan mereka dengan orang lain. Syafiq kemudiannya bertemu dengan seorang gadis buta bernama Mastura yang dilanggarnya secara tidak sengaja. Semakin hari, hubungan antara Syafiq dan Mastura menjadi semakin rapat sehingga Nancy berasa tersisih.

programme.title: Azura
programme.desc: Seorang jejaka yang berasal daripada keluarga orang berada ingin mengahwini wanita pilihannya, Azura namun ditentang ibu bapanya. Zack mengahwini Azura dan bekerja sebagai buruh untuk menyara keluarganya - ini setelah kewangannya dipotong oleh keluarga. Azura hamil namun dia mula mengesyaki bahawa bayi tersebut bukan miliknya.

programme.title: Bila Jodoh
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hasrul yang selalu gagal mencari jodoh untuk dirinya. Dengan secara tidak sengaja, dia sering bertemu Liza namun mereka sering bertikam lidah. Dalam masa yang sama, keluarga Hasrul mencari calon untuk dijodohkan dengannya. Tanpa disedari Hasrul, gadis yang ingin dikenalkan kepadanya ialah Liza.

programme.title: Azura (2012)
programme.desc: Azura, seorang gadis remaja yang gigih hadapi cabaran hidup untuk mencapai cita-citanya. Dia tinggal bersama ibu saudaranya setelah kedua ibu bapanya meninggal dunia dalam satu tragedi. Azura kemudiannya menjadi mahasiswa di sebuah universiti swasta dan menjalinkan hubungan mesra dengan Zek, seorang anak hartawan. Walau bagaimanapun, cinta mereka dihalang oleh bapa Zek dan mereka terpaksa melalui pelbagai dugaan.

programme.title: Jiran
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ramlan sekeluarga yang baru berpindah di sebuah kawasan perumahan. Namun, Ramlan melarang isteri dan anaknya Tina daripada bergaul dengan jiran-jiran mereka di situ. Ramlan sendiri beranggapan bahawa dengan berlaku sombong terhadap orang, dirinya akan dipandang mulia. Kesombongan Ramlan itu akhirnya menyusahkan dirinya sendiri apabila berlaku satu insiden yang melibatkan kehilangan Tina.

programme.title: XX Ray
programme.desc: Obsesinya terhadap angkasa lepas telah membuatkan Amir untuk mencipta sebuah topi keledar. Topi keledar ini merupakan penemuan baru apabila ia menggunakan kuasa tahi bintang. Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

Zack mengahwini Azura dan bekerja sebagai buruh untuk menyara keluarganya - ini setelah kewangannya dipotong oleh keluarga. Azura hamil namun dia mula mengesyaki bahawa bayi tersebut bukan miliknya.

programme.title: Bila Jodoh
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hasrul yang selalu gagal mencari jodoh untuk dirinya. Dengan secara tidak sengaja, dia sering bertemu Liza namun mereka sering bertikam lidah. Dalam masa yang sama, keluarga Hasrul mencari calon untuk dijodohkan dengannya. Tanpa disedari Hasrul, gadis yang ingin dikenalkan kepadanya ialah Liza.

programme.title: XX Ray
programme.desc: Obsesinya terhadap angkasa lepas telah membuatkan Amir untuk mencipta sebuah topi keledar. Topi keledar ini merupakan penemuan baru apabila ia menggunakan kuasa tahi bintang. Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

programme.title: Tembus
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hari yang memegang tanggungjawab besar dalam mengotakan janji agar kehidupan rumahtangganya menjadi semakin baik. Di mata masyarakat, Hari dan isterinya, Izza dianggap sebagai pasangan ideal yang sukses dalam hal rumahtangga dan kerjaya. Namun mereka diuji dengan kehilangan anak dan pelbagai rahsia terbongkar akibat terjadinya peristiwa itu.

programme.title: Cinta Bollywood
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Shahrul, anak Tok Penghulu merangkap seorang penganggur yang tinggal di Parit Buntar bersama keluarganya. Dia menaruh hati kepada seorang gadis bernama Asha. Pada suatu hari, seorang penerbit filem telah datang ke kampungnya untuk membuat penggambaran drama berjudul Cinta Bollywood. Shahrul kemudiannya dilantik menjadi production manager dan pelakon untuk penggambaran drama itu. Ketika penggambaran dibuat, Salman, hero drama itu semakin rapat dengan Asha dan hal ini membuatkan Shahrul cemburu.

programme.title: Cikgu Romantik
programme.desc: Bercita-cita ingin menjadi selebriti terkenal, Azizah mendapat surat uji bakat yang bertempat di Kuala Lumpur. Dia pun pergi dan menetap di rumah temannya, Tila lalu berkenalan bersama seorang guru vokal iaitu Ramli. Muncul pula Shahrul yang mengatakan bahawa raut wajah Azizah seiras dengan isterinya yang telah meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Kasih Farra
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Farra yang bercinta dengan Lokman, seorang lelaki yang jauh lebih tua daripada usianya. Lokman baru pulang ke Malaysia selepas lebih 20 tahun merantau ke luar negara. Tanpa pengetahuan Lokman, Farra ialah anak kepada bekas kekasihnya, Zura. Dalam masa yang sama, Zura sedang mencari Lokman untuk meminta maaf atas apa yang berlaku kepada hubungan mereka di masa lampau.

programme.title: Ali Setan
programme.desc: Ali pelajar universiti yang nakal dan suka bergurau berjumpa Asmidar ketika dalam perjalanan ke universiti. Ali selalu mencari jalan untuk mengusik Asmidar, lama kelamaan perasaan cinta mula berputik antara mereka berdua. Konflik mula terjadi apabila Ali sebenarnya sudah berkahwin dengan Tipah namun atas sebab terpaksa.

programme.title: Nylea & Harris
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Harris yang terpaksa bekerja sebagai pelayan walaupun dia memiliki kelulusan tinggi. Dia kemudiannya berjaya mendapat kerja sebagai arkitek di sebuah firma milik Tan Sri Kadir. Tugas pertama Harris ialah untuk menyiapkan sebuah rumah untuk anak perempuan Tan Sri Kadir iaitu Nylea. Pada mulanya Harris dan Nylea sering bertengkar namun lama kelamaan timbul bibit-bibit percintaan antara mereka berdua. Walau bagaimanapun, muncul pula Chris, bekas tunangan Nylea ke dalam hidup mereka yang membuatkan Harris sangat kecewa.

programme.title: Ali Setan 2
programme.desc: Ikatan yang ingin tercipta terpaksa dileraikan kerana campur tangan keluarga menyebabkan Ali dan Asmidar pergi membawa haluan sendiri. Rancangan untuk mendirikan rumahtangga telah diganggu oleh Jeff yang inginkan Asmidar. Ayah Asmidar pula menyuruhnya berkahwin bersama Jeff - namun setelah beberapa bulan mereka pun bercerai kerana tidak bahagia. Ali dan Asmidar pun bersatu semula.

programme.title: CNY Blessing of Formosa T Ep408
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life.This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easytounderstand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep335
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Way to Health (M) Ep336
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about ones health.

programme.title: Top Singers (T) Ep658
programme.desc: The show 'Top Singers' aims to spotlight outstanding Taiwanese singers and composers, setting a new standard in the industry. Combining elements of competition, variety, and personal stories, the show welcomes participants of all ages. Its goals include discovering grassroots talent, innovating Taiwanese song performance styles, and involving more local talent in song composition to infuse new life into Taiwanese music.

programme.title: Show Biz (M) Ep1008
programme.desc: Every second counts in "Show Biz" to bring you with the most High Speed star news, exciting live shows and performers interviews.

programme.title: Dear Mom (M) Ep40
programme.desc: Feng-Yi Li handles everything in the house while her husband, Shu-An, lounges and daydreams. She constantly worries about the love lives of their four daughters. Yi-Wan starts a relationship with a gang leaders son despite claiming to have never dated. Qing-Qing may be having an affair with a married man. Xiao-Xi is infatuated with the school team captain but is unaware of "the others." An-Qing returns from the US with her son after a failed marriage. When Feng-Yi suddenly disappears, the sisters realize they've neglected their mother, who has always supported them. Now they must find her and get their lives back on track.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: The Grandmaster
programme.desc: Directed by the acclaimed filmmaker Wong Kar Wai, this epic action feature begins in Foshan when Ip Man, the martial arts master from the south, takes up a challenge by ageing northern master Gong Yu Tian. Ip Man wins the fight, but is then defeated by Gong Yu Tians daughter Gong Er, with whom he forms an emotional bond

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: The Monkey King
programme.desc: After Goddess Nuwa sacrifices herself to save the mortal world, Monkey King comes into being from one of her crystals. Powerful and uncontrollable, Monkey King challenges the Jade Emperor and causes an uproar in heaven, unwittingly creating an opportunity for the wicked Buffalo Demon King to wage war in heaven.

programme.title: Table for Six 2
programme.desc: The sequel to "Table for Six", Bernard and Lung plan to get married while their eldest brother is away. Yet, the weddings spiral into a chaotic battleground with escalating family drama, creating a messy affair for everyone involved.

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: Fat Choi Spirit
programme.desc: Andy is a mahjong master who is very popular in the neighbourhood. However, after being cursed by his ex-girlfriend, Andy always experiences bad luck when playing mahjong. Can he finally dodge this streak of bad luck?

programme.title: 77 Heartwarmings
programme.desc: After breaking up with Adam, Eva focuses on her career but Adam still wants to make up and tries to move her 77 times. Things become more complicated when a Thai movie idol courts Eva. It is at this time that Evas mother becomes very ill, and she considers marriage in order to fulfil her mothers wish. Will Adam succeed in warming Evas heart?

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: Caught in Time
programme.desc: Based on true events, Detective Zhong Cheng leads a task force in pursuit of Eagle, a criminal gang led by Zhang Sun. Highly methodical and disciplined, the gang manages to avoid capture after each heist. A decade later, the need to stop Eagle is more urgent than ever when Zhong Cheng realizes that his time is almost up to solve the case.

programme.title: Wu Kong
programme.desc: Set 500 years before the Monkey King Wu Kong wreaks havoc in the heavenly kingdom, the movie tells the story of how Wu Kong who, unwilling to bow to his own destiny, sets out to rebel against the gods.

programme.title: Z Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk is on the case of a corrupt policeman but finds all key witnesses killed when he starts to discover some clues. As investigation continues, Luk uncovers the fraud scheme of an organized corrupt group involving the governments $15 billion Care Fund. He must fight against them to keep Hong Kong corruption free.

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Kung Fu Hustle
programme.desc: Mobster Sing aspires to join the Axe Gang. As he stumbles into a slum ruled by eccentric landlords that are kung fu masters in disguise, his actions cause the gang and the landlords to engage in an explosive kung fu battle

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong
programme.desc: Ng Shun and his family return to the public housing estate where he grew up, not to visit his aging father, but to seek refuge after his business has failed. When his family of five squeeze into the small estate unit, Ng Shun is forced to face his long-neglected family problems...

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 3
programme.desc: Gambling tycoon Man suddenly marries his new partner Sophie, which shocked his only son, Ken. In the wake of Man's heart attack, Ken must battle Sophie - who has persuaded Man to transfer his grand master title to her in the event of his death - for the rightful claim to the familys gambling business in a riveting game of mahjong.

programme.title: Chasing the Dragon
programme.desc: Infamous real-life drug kingpin Crippled Ho came to Hong Kong as an illegal immigrant in 1963 and ruthlessly built an empire from the chaotic underworld of drug dealers and corrupt police who ruled the city under notorious detective Lee Rock.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: A real estate tycoon plans to turn a marine protected area into a new property development, thereby destroying the secret habitat of the mermaids. A beautiful mermaid, Shan, is tasked to seduce the tycoon and stop the destruction. However, when Shans mission fails, a final, fatal war between humans and mermaids becomes inevitable.

programme.title: Endgame
programme.desc: A killer and a stage actor accidentally swapped their identities at a bathhouse. The actor must complete the killers mission while the killer thinks he is a hopeless actor after losing his memory during the accident. When the killer strives to become a successful stage actor, he also starts to recall what has happened

programme.title: Vanguard
programme.desc: A businessman Qin Guo Li is being kidnapped in London and his daughter is also in danger. The international security team, Vanguard, is hired to rescue them. Tang Huan Ting, the founder, gathers an elite team to track them down across countries, from London to Africa and Dubai. In the process, they also discover another dangerous conspiracy.

programme.title: Kung Fu Mahjong 2
programme.desc: Fanny appears to be an ordinary housewife but is in fact a mahjong expert. Deeply in love with her husband, she loses to a seductive woman, Curvy, both on the mahjong table and in competing for her husbands love. With the help from her mahjong master, Fanny vows to take on Curvy in the Mahjong King tournament!

programme.title: Stand Up Story
programme.desc: Mancer knows his father Wah is intellectually challenged since young and has to take care of him after his mother left them. When Mancer discovers and finds solace in stand-up comedy, he learns that hardships provide the best comedic material - from his own school ridicule experience to pandemic woes, misery can fuel laughter!

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: First Love the Litter on the Breeze
programme.desc: This movie is the directorial debut of actor Eric Kot for Wong Kar Wai. Eric features the topic of first love in his first movie: a sleepwalker guided through the night by a lonely admirer is bizarre yet romantic, while a married grocer facing the vengeful first love that he once rejected is heartbreaking.

programme.title: Maoshan Heavenly Master
programme.desc: Prisoner Chi flees away under Master Zhangs custody, causing the latter to be expelled from his clan. On his way to find Chi, Master Zhang arrives at a place where many people vanish for no reason. He soon discovers that it is Chi who captures them in his training to become a serpent demon. The war between human and demon has just begun!

programme.title: Kungfu Stuntmen
programme.desc: Hong Kong action cinema is famous for its real kung fu moves performed by a group called Kung Fu Stuntmen. This docu-film pays tribute to the generations of kung fu stuntmen, with the crew spending over two years digging archives and interviewing many talents, including the most prominent masters like Jackie Chan, Donnie Yen and Sammo Hung.

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: A real estate tycoon plans to turn a marine protected area into a new property development, thereby destroying the secret habitat of the mermaids. A beautiful mermaid, Shan, is tasked to seduce the tycoon and stop the destruction. However, when Shans mission fails, a final, fatal war between humans and mermaids becomes inevitable.

programme.title: Infernal Affairs II
programme.desc: In this prequel, the secrets of Infernal Affairs are revealed - the resentment between police superintendent Wong and crime boss Sam, as well as the beginning of the parallel fates of the two moles, Yan and Ming. The keys lie in the hands of Sam's wife, a ruthless kingpin and a righteous cop.

programme.title: Ready O/R Rot
programme.desc: Guy and Heidi are finally getting married but pressure from Guys mother creates much friction between them. Meanwhile, Grey Bear suspects his wife of cheating on him and Ken faces the biggest crisis of his life when Jessica accidentally gets pregnant. Can they eventually solve their relationship problems?

programme.title: The Lost Bladesman
programme.desc: An epic historic adventure set during the turbulent times of the Three Kingdoms. Cao Cao attempts to enlist Guan Yu into his forces, but Guan is loyal to his sworn brother Liu Bei, who is also Caos enemy. As Guan tries to rescue Liu Beis concubine from Cao, he is forced to fight his way through. Can he succeed in the end?

programme.title: The Proud Twins
programme.desc: Jiang Xiao Yu is separated from his twin brother as a baby after his parents are murdered. He is taken by a couple to Villains Valley and raised to be a villain by a host of outlaws. Jiang leaves the valley to explore the world when he grows up. Will he be able to avenge his parents and meet with his twin brother?

programme.title: THE AMOROUS LOTUS PAN
programme.desc: Adapted from the renowned Chinese novel, The Water Margin, this is the story of a poor and beautiful girl Lotus Pan, who is raped by her master and had to be married off to a midget who treats her badly. Lost and lonely, Pan unwittingly becomes a pawn in the game of lust between her husbands playboy brother Wu Song, and a murderous man Men Ching.

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: We Love Millionaires
programme.desc: In this romantic comedy, three beautiful Hong Kong salesgirls travel to Osaka in Japan to pursue their dreams of marrying a rich man. They masquerade as high society debutantes and make their way to a posh resort to meet and woo millionaires (or fake ones!).

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: Carry on Doctors and Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: The Kingdom and the Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Cheng Te meets country maiden Li Feng on a visit to Southern China. It was love at first sight and the Emperor leaves with a promise that Li Feng would be his empress. When he sends for Li one year later, she was too ill to withstand the arduous journey and arrives just in time to die in the arms of her beloved...

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu headed to Hong Kong, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned! Can he survive difficult times and finally overcome adversity?

programme.title: The Lady is the Boss
programme.desc: Wong Hsia Yuan is a traditional kung fu master whose academy is on the brink of closure. Chan Mei Ling arrives from U.S. to revitalize the academy but her way of recruiting students is going beyond questionably legal. Yuan is furious, but when the local triads enter the picture, Yuan and Ling join hands to take back the neighborhood.

programme.title: Boxer Rebellion
programme.desc: The Empress Dowager Cixi believes the Boxers claim that they have developed a kung fu that makes them impervious to weapons, thus declaring war against the alliances of eight foreign nations. The lack of weapons and good leadership in the Ching government allows the Eight Nation Alliances to take down Beijing.

programme.title: King Cat
programme.desc: The son of the imperial teacher is beheaded by Justice Bao for corruption. Infuriated, the teacher hires assassins to kill Bao, who is saved by Zhan Zhao. Meanwhile, a royal treasure is stolen while a murder takes place. Bao is ordered to solve the case in ten days and Zhan quickly sets off to investigate. Will they solve the case in time?

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brothers death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: A compulsive gambler with bad luck owes money to a violent gangster boss and trades his wife as down payment, causing her to leave him. As he decides to kill himself, a mysterious old man offers him a proposal to marry the ghost of his dead daughter in exchange for cash and an expensive apartment.

programme.title: The Human Goddess
programme.desc: This is a love story between an alluring fairy, Seventh Sister, who comes down from heaven to experience life in 70s Hong Kong, and a man who is running a debt laden orphanage. A heartless tycoon plans to take over the orphanage for its land but has to deal with Seventh Sisters magical powers as she aims to protect it from falling into his hands!

programme.title: Lady With A Sword
programme.desc: Swordswoman Feng tries to find a group of villains responsible for her eldest sister's death, but is shocked to discover that her fianc, Jin, is one of them. At the same time, Jin's mother and the two other killers are planning to kill Feng. Can Feng fight back and take her revenge?

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical comedy is about how a young man Fen, along with his buddy Hamburger, finds love and success in the advertising world.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief, who happens to be the boyfriend of one of Uncle Bills nieces!

programme.title: The 82 Tenants
programme.desc: Continuing the success of the classic comedy House of 72 tenants, this sequel tells the stories of tenants living in an old building in Hong Kong who are forced to evict by the developers. Some tenants prefer to take the compensation while some resist the move. Will the acquisitions plan destroy the harmony of the neighborhood?

programme.title: Operation Lipstick
programme.desc: A professors assistant stole a micro-film storing the secret of a newly invented nuclear reactor and sells it to a crime syndicate. However, the micro-film accidentally falls into the hands of a nightclub dancer and a thief in the process, leading to them being relentlessly pursued by the crime syndicate to retrieve the micro-film.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: Brothers Five
programme.desc: The five Kao brothers, separated since birth, are unaware that the master of Teng Lung Manor has killed their father. All five however, vow to defeat the vicious gangsters at the manor due to their bullying ways. After reuniting and with much discipline and hard work, the Kaos are prepared to face Lung and his gang.

programme.title: The Vengeful Beauty
programme.desc: The Flying Guillotine assassins are secretly working for the Emperor and its leader Jin is sent to kill Hon, who knows this secret. Hons pregnant wife Rong seeks to kill Jin but retreats to protect her unborn child. When she is hunted down herself, Rong hooks up with a former Flying Guillotine member and her martial arts senior to fight back...

programme.title: Dirty Ho
programme.desc: Master Wang, who is actually the 11th prince, poses as an antique connoisseur to hide his true identity. When he meets Dirty Ho, a witty con artist, Wang knows he has found the right man to help him untangle a royal succession plot...

programme.title: The Silver Fox
programme.desc: The formidable swordswoman Silver Fox was a child when her father was senselessly wounded by his step brother, and her mother raped. It is payback time eighteen years later, as her father trains her up with kung fu to take revenge on his behalf.

programme.title: Twin Blades Of Doom
programme.desc: A retired martial artist is forced to return with a vengeance after his family and friends are murdered by the evil Ghost Gang. He decides to challenge the gangs leader to a deadly duel so as to take revenge. Can he defeat the ruthless leader in the end?

programme.title: The Golden Seal
programme.desc: Dai Tian Chou practices martial arts since young so he can avenge his fathers death. He meets Wu Xiao Yan who is disguised as a man one day and is suddenly beaten by a group of gangsters. Wu begs her father to allow her to take Dai back home to recover. Little does Dai know this is his chance to take revenge.

programme.title: Shaolin Mantis
programme.desc: The Emperor orders Feng to find proofs of Master Tians rebellion in his house. Feng falls in love with Tians granddaughter and marries her. When he finds the proofs and tries to leave with her, his wife is killed in the fight against Tian. Feng creates the mantis-style martial arts and vows to avenge her death.

programme.title: Temple Of The Red Lotus
programme.desc: A young guy Wu, heads off to the Dragon Valley to meet his childhood friend Lian Chu, who was promised to be his bride. When he arrives, he finds out that the family of his bride may not be an entirely honest bunch of people. Wu wishes to take Lian Chu with him, so he has no choice but to fight against her family

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: When Jianying discovers the Zhao clan's fortune will be left to his brother Yulong, he engineers his parents' death and sends his own son out to kill Yulong.

programme.title: The Adulteress
programme.desc: The film is about the drugged, then disgraced wife of a peddler in the waning days of the Ching Dynasty. To make matters worse, shes soon framed for her husbands murder by her rapist, the son of the local magistrate! And even that is not the end of her woes in this emotional suspense

programme.title: The Battle Wizard
programme.desc: Dali Prince Tuan Yu knows nothing about martial arts, but leaves the palace for the martial arts world. He meets a snake sorceress and his mysterious half-sister. Through various misadventures, Tuan Yu gains invincible power by sucking the cobras blood and swallowing the magic toad, eventually defeating his fathers old rival.

programme.title: Go Dog Go! Ep37
programme.desc: The Trouble with Kibbles / Road to Kindness - When Tag asks Mom to be the pilot for the upcoming Dogcaththlon race, Mom isnt sure she is ready. Until Paw reminds her of the day she saved Pawston! Mom tells the story of how she used her blimp to save the city from an eruption at the kibble factory. / Pawston is hosting a Roller Disco Night in the park, but Frank isn't allowed to attend due to last year's poor behavior. Tag convinces Mayor Sniffington to let Frank come to the party if he passes Leo's Road to Kindness.

programme.title: Go Dog Go! Ep38
programme.desc: How Tag Got Her Tag / Blankie Blaster - Its Show and Tell Day for the Race Cadets! Tag decides to talk about how she got the race flag tag on her collar, but realizes she doesnt know the real story of how she got it. Her family launches into an epic retelling of how Tag got her tag. / Spike is about to launch into space when he calls Tag in a panic to tell her that he left his special blankie behind! He cant sleep without it! Tag, Grandmaw, and Grandpaw race off to the rocket launch to try and get it back to him.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep49
programme.desc: Bunker Break-In/To Catch a Critter - When Branch loses to Poppy at Capture the Flag, he challenges her to break into his bunker and steal Gary, to prove her abilities. Poppy organizes a whacky heist with the help of the Snack Pack. /When Smidge accidentally loses some of the critters Milton cares for, she must try and retrieve them from Trolls Forest.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep50
programme.desc: CJ Wooferbug/What Did I Miss - DJ is excited to give her niece CJ her own wooferbug for her birthday. But the wooferbug proves difficult to transport across Trolls Village. Will DJ be able to get it to CJ before CJs birthday party ends?/When Peppy takes an entire day to get a new haircut, he asks Poppy to fill him in on what he missed. What follows is a series of short sketches, as we explore an average day in Troll Village.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep49
programme.desc: The Wrath Of Morticus Khan - King Julien clones himself but things take a turn for the worse when Morticus Khan, an evil warlord, unleashes an army of Mort clones on the kingdom

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep50
programme.desc: Koto, Plain And Tall - Julien is lost in the jungle and accidentally saves a Mountain Lemur named Koto who turns out to be the biggest threat the kingdom has ever faced

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep25
programme.desc: Si - Puss fights the Duchess to retrieve the first coin he ever took from the Treasure House, which can help him restore San Lorenzo's protective spell.

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep25
programme.desc: Memory Spark / Wondertusk - Kelps learns about memory spark in an attempt to relive a memory of his grandmother. / Kelp and the underwater gang put on a show to showcase their imaginary sparks. As she practices, however, Scallop becomes convinced her tusk has a real spark!

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep25
programme.desc: Flying High / Nest Sweet Nest - Marcus makes a Dew Drop-sized hot-air balloon for Phoebe and the Dews have a blast helping their kids from above, including secretly guiding Lola back to her family, before she accidentally follows Hip-Hop the frog out of the park. / Phoebe makes a pair of glasses for Bob the bird, but when seeing things clearly for the first time gets him lost, the Dews help Bob find his nest before his family arrives for a visit.

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep25
programme.desc: Belly Flop - The Riders have to save Elbone when he's swallowed by a giant Sea Gronckle, and Dak's awful cooking might be just the thing to do it.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep25
programme.desc: The Pawston Chewbilee / Dont Go, Cat. Go! - Based on PD Eastman's classic childrens book, Go, Dog. Go! Follows 6-year-old dog, Tag Barker, on her hilarious adventures in the city of Pawston, a fun-loving community of dogs on the go. Tag is a skilled mechanic and loves anything that goes. With her ingenuity and creativity, Tag can go as far as any plan will take her, always with her best friend, Scooch Pooch, by her side. Scoochs easy-going nature is the perfect counterbalance to Tags high-octane energy. But as much as Tag loves to go, shes often reminded that it's family, friends and neighbors that really fuel a community.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep28
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Angry Abnormal Atrocities of the Astute Animal Agressors - Stuck in separate camps, Harold and George unleash a hyperintelligent talking possum to scare the pants off of Krupp. What could possibly go wrong?

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep29
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Abysmal Altercation of the Abominable Altitooth - Eager to get the campers out of his hair, Krupp orders them to climb Plummet Peak, where a terrifying creature is rumored to reside.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep30
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Bizarre Bout of the Beastly Barfilisk - Harold and George don't ask for much -- just a fun scavenger hunt that doesn't include doing Krupp's errands. Careful what you wish for, fellas.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep5
programme.desc: In Dragons We Trust - After the dragons of Berk are blamed for an outbreak of crime, Hiccup is determined to find out whats really going on before the dragons are exiled.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep6
programme.desc: Alvin & the Outcasts - Alvin and the outcast Vikings terrorize Berk, left defenseless without their dragons, and now only Hiccup can bring them back.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep7
programme.desc: How to Pick Your Dragon - Stoick wants to train his own dragon and enlists Hiccup to help him tame the most ferocious species yet.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep67
programme.desc: Inner Children - JJ reluctantly lets Tina take over her assistant duties for the day, but a Tina slip-up leads to an outbreak of town adults drinking diluted special formula that makes them all baby-brained. When JJ discovers this, she works with R & D Baby Simmons and Security Baby Katja to antidote the wobbling Adult Babies before Tina can find out and blame herself.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep68
programme.desc: Poompf! - Crispin Biscuits frames Boss and Tinas startup company for exploding baby Iggys favorite stuffed animal, and Tina is forced to the sidelines to avoid any more bad press. As Crispin expands his plan to burst all the plush toys in the neighborhood, Tina discovers she can stop this by breaking open and rewiring a single toy doll. Unfortunately that doll is Baby Corps current head honcho, Pull-String CEO Baby.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep69
programme.desc: The Heat is On - On the hottest week of the year and a miserable time for babies, Boss and Tim infiltrates a country club with a very cool splash pad in order to find some way around their strict no-babies policy. Meanwhile, Banker Baby Benny visits the startup company to check on his investment. Tina has to cover up how the heat has split her coworkers into lawless factions fighting over a fan and a mist cooler.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep14
programme.desc: Doom and Groom - Po and the team have one last attempt to get the pendant, but they will have to disrupt Jayesh's wedding, and contend with his guards, to do so. At the mage island, Klaus and Veruca get hold of the Tianshang helmet.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep15
programme.desc: The Pinging - Mr. Ping is possessed by the ghost of Master Mastodon, the ancient master sworn to protect the Tianshang storm wheels. After a ghostly sewer chase, Mastodon agrees to help our team to stop Klaus and Veruca. He reveals that their next step is to go across the sea to Central America.

programme.title: Kung Fu Panda: The Dragon Knight Ep16
programme.desc: Mister Mastodon - Po and team arrive in Guatemala and meet farmers who are facing a mysterious threat-- named The Protector, wielding the Storm Wheels.
